Pre-Game Insights: Pakistan and Ireland have been knocked out from the tournament
Ireland and Pakistan have met each other on 4 occasions in T20Is, with Pakistan winning 3 times and Ireland once
Miscellaneous Highlights: This is the first time that Pakistan has been eliminated after just 3 games of the T20 World Cup
Others: The match will be played at the Central Broward Regional Park Stadium Turf Ground, Lauderhill in Florida
Pakistan might look to bring in some changes in their playing XI and give opportunities to the players who have not got a chance so far
Ireland had not played a match for a week and hence, it might be difficult to tell if the side would make any changes
The forecast for Sunday is expected to be better, but it all will come down to how much rain falls overnight and how the outfield will be in the morning
